import React, { Component } from 'react';

import {
  StyleSheet,

  const ProfileView = (navigationProps) => {



    return (
      <ScrollView behavior="padding"> 
<View >
<View >
<Text style={styles.name}>
                  Usama

</View>
           

      <View style={styles.container}>

            </View>
          </View>

          <View style={styles.body}>

      </View>
      </View>
      </ScrollView> 
    );

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
